00:24:26.300 --> 00:24:27.540
Hindi kami bumangon.

00:24:27.980 --> 00:24:28.900
Paano ito?

00:24:29.260 --> 00:24:30.300
Pumunta ka at sabihin sa kanya.

00:24:30.660 --> 00:24:32.220
Sige, pupunta ako ngayon.

00:24:32.970 --> 00:24:33.820
Jicai,

00:24:33.820 --> 00:24:35.520
